在[[真菌學|真菌學]]中，'''伏魯寧體'''（{{lang-en|Woronin body}}）得名自[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]植物學家與真菌學家{{link-en|米哈伊爾·史蒂巴诺维契·伏魯寧|Mikhail Stepanovich Voronin}}<ref>{{cite book|title=A Dictionary of Biology|year=2004|publisher=Oxford University Press|url=http://www.encyclopedia.com/doc/1O6-Woroninbody.html|accessdate=2009-09-03|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701185318/http://www.encyclopedia.com/doc/1O6-Woroninbody.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，
是高等真菌的一種胞器，源於[[過氧化體|過氧化體]]，在顯微鏡下核心緻密，由一層膜組成，通常出現於將[[菌絲|菌絲]]分割成不同細胞的[[隔膜|隔膜]]附近。其主要功能是在受傷或老化時將隔膜孔（septal pores）堵住，以免[[細胞質|細胞質]]流出<ref>{{cite journal|title=A new self-assembled peroxisomal vesicle required for efficient resealing of the plasma membrane|pages=226–231|issn=1465-7392|journal=Nature Cell Biology|volume=2|issue=4|date=2000-4|doi=10.1038/35008652|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10783241|accessdate=2019-02-12|author=G. Jedd, N. H. Chua|archive-date=2020-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511162232/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10783241|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=A HEX-1 crystal lattice required for Woronin body function in Neurospora crassa|pages=264–270|issn=1072-8368|journal=Nature Structural Biology|volume=10|issue=4|date=2003-4|doi=10.1038/nsb910|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12640443|accessdate=2019-02-12|author=Ping Yuan, Gregory Jedd, Desigan Kumaran, Subramanyam Swaminathan, Helen Shio, David Hewitt, Nam-Hai Chua, Kunchithapadam Swaminathan|archive-date=2020-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511162235/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12640443|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

